.be/de\">Satellic</a></li><li><a href=\"https://axxes.fr/de\">Axxès</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.eurotoll.eu/fr\">Eurotoll</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.telepass.com/en/truck#\">Telepass</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.as24.com/nl\">Total</a></li><li><a href=\"https://toll4europe.eu/de\">Toll4Europe</a></li></ul>","nl":"<p>De kilometerheffing wordt berekend met behulp van een <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/kilometerheffing/on-board-unit-obu\">‘On Board Unit’ (OBU)</a>. Dit toestel registreert tot op de meter de gereden kilometers.</p><h3>Controle en boetes</h3><p>Om te controleren of weggebruikers in orde zijn, doet Viapass in samenwerking met de 3 gewesten controles in België. Als er een overtreding wordt vastgesteld, betaalt u een boete. <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/kilometerheffing/boetes-in-de-kilometerheffing\">Dit is een variabele boete, afhankelijk van de ernst van de boete.</a></p>"},"@type":"Procedure","order":0}],"websites":[{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-formal":"Satellic","nl":"Satellic","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Satellic"},"url":"https://www.satellic.be/nl","@type":"Website","order":0},{"naam":{"nl":"Eurotoll ","nl-BE-x-formal":"Eurotoll ","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Eurotoll "},"url":"https://www.eurotoll.eu/fr","@type":"Website","order":1},{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-formal":"Viapass","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Viapass","nl":"Viapass"},"url":"https://www.viapass.be","@type":"Website","order":2},{"naam":{"nl":"TOTAL","nl-BE-x-formal":"TOTAL","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"TOTAL"},"url":"https://www.as24.com/nl","@type":"Website","order":3},{"naam":{"nl":"Toll4Europe","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Toll4Europe","nl-BE-x-formal":"Toll4Europe"},"url":"https://toll4europe.eu/de","@type":"Website","order":4},{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-formal":"Telepass ","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Telepass ","nl":"Telepass "},"url":"https://www.telepass.com/en/truck#","@type":"Website","order":5},{"naam":{"nl":"Viapass - Deutsch","de":"Viapass - Deutsch","nl-BE-x-f